      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TRUNKEY MINK (7) doesn't have the best strike-rate but recent form is sound. Finished second (29.95) at this track last time making it four minors on end. Form at the trip sound including two wins. Form from her last run is proving to be solid. Ready to find winning form. FIREBALL NIGHT (8) was an impressive winner last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 2.25 lengths (15.74) at The Gardens. Solid beginner and with a good start should have clear running out wide. Bold showing expected again. BIG RED MIYAGI (1) was unfavoured last start but gave a huge sight when led for much of the way to place (22.89) at this track in a Mix 3/4 over 388m. Leading chance. GOOD ODDS TURBO (4) is always hard to beat when he races here at this trip.",
